The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Bengal captaincy
                                                                                                                                                                                                     Bengal captaincy
            A STAFF REPORTER                      
	Calcutta: The Cricket Association of Bengal (CAB) will offer Sourav Ganguly the Bengal captaincy for Ranji Trophy.         
	According to CAB joint secretary, Arun Mitra, Souravs inclusion matters a lot for the team.         
	I will definitely speak to him about playing the matches and, above all, offer him the captaincy, Mitra said on Tuesday.                                                                                                                          
